# TextFormatter Plus

Professional text formatting and validation utilities for Python developers.

## ðŸš€ Features

### Text Formatting
- Convert text to title case
- Convert to snake_case
- Reverse text
- Capitalize words
- Remove whitespace

### Validation
- Email validation
- Phone number validation
- Strong password validation

## ðŸ“¦ Installation

```bash
pip install textformatter-plus
```

## ðŸ’» Usage

```python
from my_feature_package import TextFormatter, Validator

# Text Formatting
formatter = TextFormatter()
result = formatter.to_title_case("hello world")
print(result)  # "Hello World"

# Validation
validator = Validator()
is_valid = validator.is_email("user@example.com")
print(is_valid)  # True
```

